tolimae, with type locality in Rio Toché, Quindio Andes, Tolima, Colombia, is currently subsumed under A. 
<taxonomicName box="[1200,1281,807,840]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Melanomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="195" pageNumber="474" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="affinis">affinis</taxonomicName>
